window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>The complete Horned Mage collection!&nbsp;</p> <p>Caleb Marshal was born with a pair of antlers, and despite having an abundance of magic, can't use any of it - thanks to a curse. Since he's majoring in magical theory at college, this is a bit of a problem. Breaking his curse, however, throws him into danger.&nbsp;</p> <p>Caleb must deal with his new powers, supernatural threats, and an ever more complicated love life. All while trying to balance a job and maintain his GPA!&nbsp;</p>"; 
